name: Here I Come Falling
description: '''Here I Come Falling''' was an American [[post-hardcore]] band from [[Springfield, Missouri]], formed in 2005. They were signed to [[Rise Records]] in 2007. They released one album, ''Oh Grave, Where Is Thy Victory'', on January 8, 2008. The album charted at number 46 on the Top ''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]'' [[Billboard charts#Albums|Christian Albums]]. They broke up in August 2008. They stated lineup changes and "other troubles" as the reason for the breakup.
